{"tid":984425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《英雄聯盟》R社主管參訪騰訊大樓 推特竟撰「騰訊是我爸爸」","createTime":"2019-01-16T19:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T02:25:55.000Z","uid":150609,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d827b0628211ff4e40cc6612d85d0d392dd3c4","tid":984425,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"本月初騰訊大動作宣布與Riot Games合資成立「騰競體育」，將旗下MOBA遊戲《英雄聯盟》業務獨立出來，成為市場化主體公司，時隔不久，Riot Games遊戲數據主管Riot Blaustoise來到中國進行例行交流，更在個人推特張貼騰訊大樓推文並附註：「Hi dad!」，可能是怕「騰訊爸爸」看不懂，他再度推了「Tencent shi wo de baba」（騰訊是我的爸爸）一文，然而「爸爸」並未回覆任何內容，他又將推文刪除，實在有夠尷尬。<br />\n<br />\nRiot Blaustoise是《英雄聯盟》的遊戲數據主管，經常會在個人推特發布有關遊戲的數據調查。1月14日當天，Riot Blaustoise個人推特被截圖一張他貼出騰訊大樓的圖文，並附註：「Hi dad!」這當然是意指中國騰訊是Riot Games實質擁有者與最大股東，叫聲「爹地」或許不過分吧！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AM1uvPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAM1uvPx.jpg&h=85e0e9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRiot Blaustoise在個人推特張貼騰訊大樓推文並附註：「Hi dad!」<br />\n</div><br />\n而在1小時後，Riot Blaustoise推特又被人發現再度推出一則純文字推文「Tencent shi wo de baba」（騰訊是我的爸爸），一篇推文可能是有玩笑成分，但連續兩篇又特別切換為拼音，可就有點「舔」啦。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyiXEH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyiXEH0.jpg&h=44a8220e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n或許是因為「爸爸」並未在兩篇推文留下任何回覆，抑或是Riot Blaustoise自覺內容有些過頭，當日傍晚默默將推文刪掉。儘管現在已經無法在他的動態牆上發現這兩則推文，但也有些網友很不客氣地回貼已截圖的證據，更留言&rdquo; whosyourdaddy&rdquo;作為嘲諷，實在是尷尬至極。<br />\n<br />\n 用力奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1525d81e0658392d00b0ae98c88d952c96d41f1","tid":984425,"uid":55493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"Greedisgood 99999999"},{"pid":"07cb1d194f9ab2b4f96e0cfddfe95726133b3cea","tid":984425,"uid":73404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1525d81e0658392d00b0ae98c88d952c96d41f1","tid":984425,"uid":55493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"Greedisgood 99999999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:16:25.000Z","msg":"thereisnospoon"},{"pid":"0ddd08a8ff7f8bc16f6783fafae0659a101e42a6","tid":984425,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:28:51.000Z","msg":"佢冇做錯 佢做自己姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bb78a3cfe669dd14045f1f2a3e7bc685f25931","tid":984425,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:21:34.000Z","msg":"港豬罷玩lol未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0578632279bba93aec6d8fee5546ba57c83dfbbe","tid":984425,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b508f3ddd68a136e1b9eea9726424dce0e994ece","tid":984425,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"iseedeadpeople"}]}